snippet.title: YOU DON'T KNOW JACK HEADRUSH Trailer
snippet.description: Were you a teen in the late 90s? If you didn't play HeadRush back then, now's the perfect time! Tons of trivia about the teen-y topics of the day await your now-aging brain and fingers! Forget everything you know about a YOU DON'T KNOW JACK game because YDKJ's horribly deformed, mutant offspring HEADRUSH has been birthed!
